Package: SigPoisProcess
Type: Package
Title: Poisson process factorization for mutational signature analysis with genomic covariates
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Alessandro", "Zito",
      email = "azito@hsph.harvard.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Implements the Poisson Process Factorization method for mutational signature 
    analysis with genomic covariates, as described by Zito, Parmigiani, and Miller (2025). 
    This package enables flexible analysis of mutational signatures using an inhomogeneous 
    Poisson point process where various genomic features shape the intensity function 
    along the genome.
